"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.10.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.10.2</span> 标题：冠冕、王冠（crown）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：כֶּתֶר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kether)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:11\">EST 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:17\">EST 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:8\">EST 6:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：נֵזֶר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：nezer)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:10\">2SA 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:12\">2KI 11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:11\">2CH 23:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:40\">PSA 89:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:18\">PSA 132:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:24\">PRO 27:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:16\">ZEC 9:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עטר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘atar（动词）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:6\">PSA 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:11\">SNG 3:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עֲטָרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘atarah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:30\">2SA 12:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr20:2\">1CH 20:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:15\">EST 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:4\">PSA 21:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:11\">SNG 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:18\">JER 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:12\">EZK 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:31\">EZK 21:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:11\">ZEC 6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:14\">ZEC 6:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：διάδημα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：diadēma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:3\">ISA 62:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:3\">REV 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:1\">REV 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:12\">REV 19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EsthGr1:11\">ESG 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EsthGr2:17\">ESG 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EsthGr8:15\">ESG 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis5:16\">WIS 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis18:24\">WIS 18:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir11:5\">SIR 11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir47:6\">SIR 47:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:9\">1MA 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:15\">1MA 6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc8:14\">1MA 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:13\">1MA 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:13\">1MA 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:54\">1MA 11:54</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc12:39\">1MA 12:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:32\">1MA 13:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd4:30\">1ES 4:30</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：στέφανος, στεφανόω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：stefanos, stefanoō（动词）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:29\">MAT 27:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:17\">MRK 15:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:2\">JHN 19:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:5\">JHN 19:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:7\">HEB 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:9\">HEB 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:4\">REV 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:10\">REV 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:2\">REV 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:7\">REV 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:1\">REV 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14\">REV 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir40:4\">SIR 40:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir45:12\">SIR 45:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:20\">1MA 10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:29\">1MA 10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:35\">1MA 11:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:37\">1MA 13:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:39\">1MA 13:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc14:4\">2MA 14:4</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0943_crown_king.jpg\" alt=\"戴王冠的国王\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">戴王冠的国王 (© CNG Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>王冠是国王或王后佩戴的一种头饰，作为王室的标志。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>“王冠”可以描述为：“他／她权力的象征，戴在他／她的头上”。</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0963_crown_thorns.jpg\" alt=\"耶稣戴着荆棘冠冕的头像\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">耶稣戴着荆棘冠冕的头像 (© Sgconlaw - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>在有些经文中，王冠只是作为国王或王后地位的象征。如果有些文化是用其他象征物来表示王室（或最高领袖）的地位，则可以用那些象征来替代“王冠”。举例来说，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:17\">EST 2:17</a> 可以译为，“他把皇家的印赐给她，立她为王后，代替瓦实提。”同样，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:4\">PSA 21:4</a> （《和》21:3）可译为，“你把他安放在酋长的凳子上”或“你立他为首领”。</p>\n<p>在有些经文中（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:9\">JOB 19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:36\">JOB 31:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:4\">PRO 12:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:31\">PRO 16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:6\">PRO 17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:16\">LAM 5:16</a> ），很难根据上下文清楚确定希伯来文<em>&#x27;atarah</em> 是指王冠还是花环（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">6.8 花环、王冠 (wreath, crown)&lt;REALIA:6.8&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:13\">1MA 11:13</a> 原文字面意为：“然后，多利买进入安提阿，并戴上亚细亚王冠。因此，他把两个王冠放在他的头上，即埃及王冠和亚细亚王冠。”<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 采用了直译。然而，这种字面翻译可能会让读者联想到一幅相当愚蠢的画面。当然，冠冕只是代表多利买在这两个地区拥有统治权。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 避免了读者以为那个国王正在努力平衡他头上戴着的两个王冠的滑稽场面，英文直译为：“多利买进入安提阿城，在那里他为自己加冕，成为叙利亚和埃及的王。”然而，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 的译法可能会让读者误以为他是同时成为叙利亚和埃及的国王的。所以，也许这样翻译更好：“多利买进入安提阿城，在那里他把自己加冕为王。这意味着他现在同时统治着埃及和叙利亚。”</p>\n<p>翻译者需要注意，戴在耶稣头上的“荆棘冠冕”是一个用荆棘枝子做成的花环（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:29\">MAT 27:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:17\">MRK 15:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:2\">JHN 19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:5\">JHN 19:5</a> ）。这件事可以描述为：“在他的头上放上一圈荆棘”，或“将带刺的枝子编成花环（或译：环），戴在他的头上。”</p>\n<p>关于<em>stefanos</em> 意指花环，参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">6.8 花环、王冠 (wreath, crown)&lt;REALIA:6.8&gt;</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
